Package: veil
Version: __VERSION__
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: aofusa <aofusa@localhost>
Depends: openssl, libc6 (>= 2.28), adduser | shadow
Description: High-performance reverse proxy server using io_uring and rustls
 Veil is a Linux-native high-performance reverse proxy supporting
 HTTP/1.1, HTTP/2, HTTP/3, kTLS, Proxy-Wasm, and advanced security
 features (seccomp, Landlock).
